### Ceramix API — REST Client
### Instala la extensión "REST Client" (humao.rest-client) para usar este archivo
### Abre el archivo, haz clic en "Send Request" sobre cualquier bloque

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  WORKSHOPS
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Obtener todos los talleres
GET {{baseUrl}}/workshops
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Crear un taller
POST {{baseUrl}}/workshops
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Taller de Prueba",
  "description": "Descripción del taller",
  "maxStudents": 10,
  "price": 1200.00,
  "category": 1,
  "instructorId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

###

### Buscar taller por título
GET {{baseUrl}}/workshops/search?title=Torno
Content-Type: application/json

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  INSTRUCTORS
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Obtener todos los instructores
GET {{baseUrl}}/instructors
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Crear instructor
POST {{baseUrl}}/instructors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "María González",
  "email": "maria@ceramix.com",
  "phone": "809-555-0101",
  "dateOfBirth": "1985-03-12T00:00:00Z",
  "specialty": "Wheel Throwing",
  "yearsOfExperience": 10,
  "bio": "Ceramista profesional con 10 años de experiencia."
}

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  STUDENTS
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Obtener todos los estudiantes
GET {{baseUrl}}/students
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Crear estudiante
POST {{baseUrl}}/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Ana Torres",
  "email": "ana@email.com",
  "phone": "809-555-0201",
  "dateOfBirth": "1998-05-20T00:00:00Z",
  "level": 0,
  "emergencyContact": "Pedro Torres 809-555-9001",
  "notes": ""
}

###

### Buscar estudiante
GET {{baseUrl}}/students/search?term=Ana
Content-Type: application/json

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  ENROLLMENTS
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Obtener todas las inscripciones
GET {{baseUrl}}/enrollments
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Crear inscripción
POST {{baseUrl}}/enrollments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workshopId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "studentId":  "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

###

### Confirmar inscripción
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/enrollments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Cancelar inscripción
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/enrollments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "El estudiante no puede asistir"
}

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  PIECES
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Obtener todas las piezas
GET {{baseUrl}}/pieces
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Piezas listas para hornear
GET {{baseUrl}}/pieces/ready-for-firing
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Crear pieza
POST {{baseUrl}}/pieces
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cuenco #1",
  "description": "Cuenco decorativo hecho en torno",
  "studentId":  "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "workshopId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "technique": 1,
  "weightGrams": 320
}

###

### Iniciar secado
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/pieces/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/start-drying
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Marcar como seca
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/pieces/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/mark-dried
Content-Type: application/json

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  FIRINGS
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Obtener todos los horneos
GET {{baseUrl}}/firings
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Crear horneo
POST {{baseUrl}}/firings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Horneo Bisque Enero",
  "type": 0,
  "kilnTemperatureCelsius": 980,
  "durationHours": 8,
  "instructorId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "plannedStartDate": "2025-02-01T10:00:00Z"
}

###

### Añadir pieza al horneo
POST {{baseUrl}}/firings/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/pieces
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pieceId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

###

### Iniciar horneo
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/firings/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/start
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Finalizar horneo
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/firings/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/finish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Todas las piezas salieron bien"
}

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  PAYMENTS
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Obtener todos los pagos
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Registrar pago
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enrollmentId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "amount": 1500.00,
  "method": 1
}

###

### Confirmar pago
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/payments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionReference": "TXN-CC-001-2025"
}

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  REPORTS
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Dashboard stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/dashboard
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Reporte de talleres
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/workshops
Content-Type: application/json
